{"TopicId":156848,"ForumId":69,"TopicTitle":"big craft crashing","CreatedByName":"rockets-don\u0026#039;t-make-toast","CreatedById":171798,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-02-23T00:28:44Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"rockets-don\u0026#039;t-make-toast","CreatedById":171798,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-02-23T00:28:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\ni have a craft with 256 detachable satellites and thousands of parts. it keeps running at 2 fps and it crashes 90% of the time. is there any way to stop it from crashing without getting a smaller craft?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-02-23T00:32:11Z\u0022 title=\u002202/23/2017 12:32  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EFebruary 23, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by rockets-don\u0026#039;t-make-toast\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"IncongruousGoat","CreatedById":157062,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-02-23T01:26:27Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTurn every graphics and physics setting you can find all the way down and try and clear up as much RAM as possible. Can\u0027t tell you more without knowing more about your install and setup.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DrLicor","CreatedById":165712,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-02-23T21:07:59Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nRun in \u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/76031-less-memory-usage-by-using-opengl/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003Eopen-gl mode\u003C/a\u003E or force it to open it in \u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/95837-forcing-directx11-40-memory-reduction/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003EDX11.\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0\u003Cbr\u003E\nAlso set your graphics to the lowest for a while.\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}